*Wakes up
Today I'm going to do [A, B,..., Z]. =) 

Ok. Let's start with A.
No. 
B? No!
What about [...]?
No motivation... 
....
End of the day:
I didn't do anything. =(

This is the "what I wanted but at the same time NOT what I wanted" - Paradox. 

#depression #mentalhealth
